Our client is a global healthcare agency, news publisher and data analytics provider specializing in the insurance industry.

Job Description
The aim of the ICT circle is to ensure that technology contributes optimally to the success of our company. With 14 colleagues you ensure that this is achieved. You also regularly join other circles to make optimal use of your expertise.

Circle ICT consists of several scrum teams. These scrum teams are each responsible for the management and further development of one or more business applications. You start as a member of scrum teams Online and CRM. You ensure that the daily operation runs smoothly and user wishes are realized. With your contribution you help to realize our marketing ambitions. It is also possible to contribute in other scrum teams. Your responsibilities include:

ensuring successful implementation of changes including optimal adoption;
2nd and 3rd line support;
assess wishes or identify improvements;
developing user stories;
to test

