8% holiday allowance, travel allowance, pension scheme and 25 vacation days per year based on a 40-hour working week;
a laptop with which you can work from home or work at the office
a position with various challenges and growth opportunities at a strong brand that is part of a growing multinational;
a good, informal working atmosphere, with regular team outings, drinks and fun parties (coronaproof);
a welcome pack so you can get started right away.

